timeline.bodyText:
I think that lines 86-87 should be replaced with:
TruststoreProvider provider = session.getProvider(TruststoreProvider.class);

This is more proper use of KeycloakSession SPI and at the same time, it is not hardcoded to "file" provider - the users can in theory replace the "file" provider with something else

